title: (Buena Vista) Eliades Ochoa - Grandes Exitos [FLAC] TQMP
description:
Eliades Ochoa y el Cuarteto Patria - Grandes Exitos (Greatest Hits)
2000

Brought to you by TQMP
The Quality Music Project

A collection of tracks pre Buena Vista Social Club. This album compiles tracks from 5 studio albums before 1997, the year BVSC was recorded. This compilation clearly shows why Eliades Ochoa was called on board the BVSC project. If you are new to his music this might be a great place to start. If you are a fan you will love it, plus there's a treat wating in line ;) - On my recent trip home I managed to find 3 of the pre BVSC studio albums which I'll be releasing in time. Stay in touch!

May the Flying Spaghetti Monster bless Eliades in eternity!
Ramen!
